	1. P9_42, as the output pin of the program, I have added "-OUT_DRIVE 2", in order to decrease the pin drive strength to 2mA from default 8mA and thus make a clock output be more square (earlier it was over- and undershooting the two voltage levels and thus the wave was too sine-y)







